/--
Paper Theorem 3 weighted-objective endpoint with both Proposition 5 cost
threshold constructions carried on positive interior intervals.

This is the source-Gaussian-friendly analogue of
`paper_theorem3_source_conditions_of_proposition5_merit_crossings_weighted_objectives_capacity_and_theorem2_fixed_pool_weighted_group_merit_formulas`:
the sub-full threshold is produced on
`Set.Icc (subFullLeftCost g) (subFullRightCost g)`, and the full-sub low/high
thresholds are produced on
`Set.Icc (fullSubLeftCost g) (fullSubRightCost g)`.
-/
theorem
    paper_theorem3_source_conditions_of_proposition5_merit_crossings_weighted_objectives_capacity_and_theorem2_fixed_pool_weighted_group_merit_formulas_subFull_fullSub_interval
